metadata.name: Swollen Bags Vol. 1
metadata.description:
He tossed and turned. These Floridian nights were hot and sticky. Half awake, two cold coins on each eyelid cooled his closed eyes.

A light went off next to his bed.  His phone.  He picked it up.  Another twitter sext.  He opened the photo. "Eh, not bad."  It was the 45th he'd seen today.  

He threw his phone back on the nightstand and turned over to go back to sleep. As he turned, something long and hard jutted against his abdomen. He grew excited. His fellow ape must have stayed after the surfing lesson.

"Oh, wait-"

He remembered he had had a long day of surfing and lazily tossed his board in the bed. Nothing to see here. Once again, cucked. His friend must have left.

Then some rustling in the sheets.  Rays of moonlight reflected off a visor, a party hat appeared. The other ape sat up, erect, still in bed.

"Looks like the surfs not the only thing that's up..."
